name: Journey Of The Giant Sandhill Crane
description:
Cranes are known to mate for life. Their elaborate ‘crane dances’ have inspired art, dancers, and choreographers. In Egypt, the double-headed crane symbol denotes prosperity.

The cultural meanings of the cranes represents ancient symbols of good fortune, happiness, longevity, creativity and eternal youth.
